Testing the API
Create a Genre:

mutation {
    createGenre(name: "Action") {
        genre {
          id
          name
        }
    }
}

Update a Genre:
mutation {
    updateGenre(id: 1, name: "Adventure") {
        genre {
          id
          name
        }
    }
}

Delete a Genre:
mutation {
    deleteGenre(id: 1) {
        success
    }
}

Fetch Movies by Genre:
query {
    moviesByGenre(genreId: 1) {
      id 
      title
      description
    }
}

Fetch Genre by Movie:
query {
    genreByMovie(movieId: 1) {
      id
      name
    }
}




